<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="textpart" subtype="poem" n="82">
<ab> <title>LXXXII.  DE VENERABILI GLVCERIO EPISCOPO. </title> </ab>
          <l n="1"><milestone unit="para"/>Suffusus minio perque optima facta rubescens  </l>
            <l n="2"><choice><sic>Yirginei</sic><corr>Virginei</corr></choice> uultus Glycerius sequitur.  </l>
            <l n="3">Puram sanguineo maculat dum rore figuram,  </l>
            <l n="4">Picta genas facies simpliciter placuit.  </l>
            <l n="5">Candentem crocea gestans aspargine frontem,  </l>
            <l n="6">Laeta uerecundis tinxerat ora notis.  </l>
            <l n="7">Indeptus sceptrum, tribuit quod testis imago,  </l>
            <l n="8">Purpura quem mentis prodidit imperio,  </l>
            <l n="9">Hinc abiit: populus paruo uix tempore felix,  </l>
            <l n="10">Sed rursus magni missus ad obsequium.  </l> 

          

